| Feature | CEP (Robust) | UXP (Fragile) |
|---------|--------------|---------------|
| **Sequence detection** | ✅ `checkSequenceOpen()` with retries | ⚠️ Simple `getActiveSequence()` single attempt |
| **Get sequence info** | ✅ `getActiveSequence()` in ExtendScript | ✅ `getActiveSequence()` in utils.js (but simpler) |
